                                        <li>**Food Industry:** Detailed product descriptions (e.g., "organic gluten-free sourdough bread"), recipe pages ("easy weeknight vegan pasta recipe"), nutritional information pages. Keyword research focuses on product names, dietary needs ("best keto snacks"), recipe types ("chicken curry recipes"), and local searches ("best sushi restaurant near me").</li>

                                    </ul>

                                </li>

