                                        <li>**Keyword Strategy:** Mix of broad keywords ("healthy snacks") and long-tail, high-intent keywords ("buy gluten-free sourdough online", "delivery pizza near me").</li>

                                        <li>**Ad Formats:** Google Shopping Ads for products, local search ads for restaurants, image and video ads to showcase appetizing food.</li>

