                            <p>In both fashion/luxury and food industries, the **customer experience (CX)** is paramount—often as important as the product itself. **Relationship marketing** extends beyond a single transaction to build enduring loyalty, foster advocacy, and maximize customer lifetime value (CLTV) among a brand's most valuable clients.</p>

