                                <li>**Fashion/Luxury:** Focus on ethical sourcing of materials (e.g., conflict-free diamonds, responsibly harvested leather), fair labor practices in supply chains, circular design initiatives (e.g., recycling programs for clothing), and reducing environmental impact of production.</li>

                                <li>**Food Industry:** Emphasizes sustainable farming practices, animal welfare, waste reduction throughout the supply chain, responsible water usage, fair trade certifications for ingredients, and supporting local farmer communities or food banks.</li>

